    <%- include('partials/header') %>

    <main class="page">
        <div class="page-text">
            <h1>Taylor Swift</h1>
            <p>
                Taylor Swift is a famous singer-songwriter who started in country music
                and later moved into pop. She is well known for turning real life
                experiences into songs that tell detailed stories.
            </p>
            <p>
                Her albums are often described as “eras” because each one has its own
                style, colours, and themes. Fans enjoy following these eras and seeing
                how her music and personality grow over time.
            </p>

            <h3>Popular Songs</h3>
            <ul>
                <li>"Love Story"</li>
                <li>"Blank Space"</li>
                <li>"Shake It Off"</li>
                <li>"Anti-Hero"</li>
            </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="page-image">
            <img src="/images/taylor.jpg"
                 alt="Taylor Swift"
                 class="profile-img">
        </div>
    </main>
